## Simple Coding Example

### AI Strategy Engine (Pseudo Code)

```python
class TradingStrategy:
    def __init__(self, risk_level):
        self.risk_level = risk_level

    def analyze_market(self, market_data):
        signal = self.ai_model(market_data)
        return signal

    def ai_model(self, data):
        if data["trend"] == "bullish" and data["volume"] > threshold:
            return "BUY"
        elif data["trend"] == "bearish":
            return "SELL"
        return "HOLD"

    def execute(self, signal):
        if signal == "BUY":
            return "Execute Buy Order"
        elif signal == "SELL":
            return "Execute Sell Order"
        return "No Action"
